# 🗺️ Roadmap

## ✅ Completed
- Core agent framework (single-agent loop)
- Memory integration (vector-based memory + retrieval)
- Tool API with plug-and-play architecture
- LLM integration (OpenAI, Anthropic, HuggingFace)
- Task execution via goal-driven plans
- Basic CLI support for interaction

## 🚧 In Progress
- Multi-agent coordination engine
- Tree-of-Thoughts planner
- Prompt optimization interface
- Enhanced evaluation suite

## 🔜 Planned
- Visual dashboard for live agent monitoring
- Support for local models (e.g. LLaMA, Mistral)
- Autonomous agent scheduling
- Deployment templates (Docker, Lambda, etc.)
- Fine-tuned model integration for domain-specific agents
